      %header
        %h1 Services
        %p
          %ul
            %li
              Complete website design and development
              %p
                Get your business online quickly. I work with designers locally or if you already have a design I can develop and host it for you. I'll take care of all the details and it doesn't have to cost you an arm and a leg.
            %li
              Mobile applications
              %p 
                Got an app idea? Want your website to run as an app? I can build an app for you that will work on all major smartphones and the iPad using the 
                %a{:href => "http://www.phonegap.com"} Phonegap 
                platform
        %p
          Sometimes you're not exactly sure what you want. I work fast and don't mind throwing away ideas and starting from scratch. I'm a fan of the Agile way of working where customer and developer are in regular communication. Pace of development is rapid and risk is low.
          
    %article
